555
00:55:05,250 --> 00:55:06,540
From Pakistan.

556
00:55:06,625 --> 00:55:07,999
Oh, wow, that's fantastic.

557
00:55:08,083 --> 00:55:11,165
Then you're our
extra-special guest. Look..

558
00:55:11,250 --> 00:55:14,915
