563
00:55:21,916 --> 00:55:22,999
Come with me.

564
00:55:23,083 --> 00:55:24,999
lf you get caught up in his chatter,
it'll be nightfall soon.

565
00:55:25,083 --> 00:55:26,832
Move aside.
- Okay, never mind me.

