father and mother.

591
00:57:08,333 --> 00:57:10,165
We don't have any
children of our own.

592
00:57:11,583 --> 00:57:18,415
So, it's just the three of us.
Look, your plait is ready.

593
00:57:21,083 --> 00:57:25,332
